    s = list(s)
    t = list(t)
    s.sort()
    t.sort()
    return s == t

import sys

def can_eq(s, t):
    if len(s) != len(t):
        return False
    for c in s:
        if c not in t:
            return False
        t = t.replace(c, '', 1)
    return True
